It was an empty city. Sara was running through the city that was once her home. She gasped. Her home... was destroyed. She tried to look for her friends. They were nowhere to be seen. Except for one...

"Tails!" she exclaimed. She ran toward Tails, only to find out it was the Tails Doll. She ran back where she came from. But she wasn't fast enough.

"Ready for Round 1?" said a voice. It was none other than Sonic.exe! Claws reached for her face...
